</p></sec><sec id="Sec4"><title>Primer design</title><p>To design primers, central parts of shiga toxin genes were used as template. Features in the designed primers such as GC content, Tm, &#x00394;G, etc. were checked by Oligo Explorer 1.1.0 and OligoAnalyzer 3.1 softwares. Two sets of primers are illustrated in Table&#x000a0;<xref rid="Tab2" ref-type="table">2</xref>. All primers were synthesized by Sigma company.<table-wrap id="Tab2"><label>Table&#x000a0;2</label><caption><p>Target genes and primer sequences used in this study</p></caption><table frame="hsides" rules="groups"><thead><tr><th align="left">Target gene</th><th align="left">GenBank accession <italic>n</italic>
